headline: Lisa Detanna Named to Barron’s 2025 List of Top 100 Financial Advisors
summary: BEVERLY HILLS, Calif., May 29, 2025--The Global Wealth Solutions Group of Raymond James is proud to announce that Lisa Detanna, Private Wealth Advisor and Managing Director, has been named to Barron’s prestigious 2025 Top 100 Financial Advisors list. The list, which recognizes top advisors across the country, was released online May 9, 2025.
